[
  {
    "startTime": 2.9,
    "endTime": 4.5,
    "text": "Hello, I'm Ira Glass."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.6,
    "endTime": 7.8,
    "text": "Welcome to another episode of my new podcast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.2,
    "endTime": 10.2,
    "text": "Friends. Who needs them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.3,
    "endTime": 11.600000000000001,
    "text": "You do!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.9,
    "endTime": 14.5,
    "text": "This week's challenge: Put yourself out there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.6,
    "endTime": 17.4,
    "text": "When a hand of friendship is offered to you, take it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.5,
    "endTime": 18.6,
    "text": "You can do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.0,
    "endTime": 21.7,
    "text": "Now, go. Make some friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.6,
    "endTime": 36.4,
    "text": "Make friends. Check."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "Nice to meet you, Shelly and Sandy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.2,
    "endTime": 46.6,
    "text": "How was your day?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.7,
    "endTime": 48.6,
    "text": "Oh, you want me to start?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.7,
    "endTime": 50.5,
    "text": "How polite, Sandy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.8,
    "endTime": 75.2,
    "text": "I gotta warn you: It's got gummy worms, tater tots, and ketchup leather."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.6,
    "endTime": 78.5,
    "text": "I know! No liverwurst."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.6,
    "endTime": 80.39999999999999,
    "text": "It's not like me to forget the protein."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.1,
    "endTime": 84.6,
    "text": "Yeah, I get it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.7,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Nobody likes my sandwiches."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.3,
    "endTime": 91.3,
    "text": "Whoa!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 105.8,
    "text": "Is that peppercorn?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.1,
    "endTime": 107.1,
    "text": "Sand!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.4,
    "endTime": 109.4,
    "text": "There you are!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.3,
    "endTime": 114.0,
    "text": "This mangy stray's done enough damage for today; he's coming with me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.1,
    "endTime": 115.39999999999999,
    "text": "He's not a stray."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.5,
    "endTime": 117.1,
    "text": "Is he your dog?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.2,
    "endTime": 118.8,
    "text": "He's, like, totally mine!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.9,
    "endTime": 120.0,
    "text": "If you want to be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.1,
    "endTime": 121.6,
    "text": "I'd like that very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.7,
    "endTime": 124.7,
    "text": "Okay, then. What's his name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.8,
    "endTime": 126.1,
    "text": "I don't have one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.2,
    "endTime": 127.60000000000001,
    "text": "He... his name's..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.4,
    "endTime": 131.20000000000002,
    "text": "... Snacks!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.3,
    "endTime": 133.0,
    "text": "- What?  - Snacks?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.1,
    "endTime": 135.79999999999998,
    "text": "Uh... I mean, Scooby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.9,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "Middle name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.7,
    "endTime": 138.7,
    "text": "Dooby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.8,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "Last name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.9,
    "endTime": 142.9,
    "text": "Doo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.2,
    "endTime": 144.39999999999998,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.5,
    "endTime": 148.6,
    "text": "If the dog has a middle name... there's no punishment for damages or theft."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.7,
    "endTime": 150.89999999999998,
    "text": "I don't like it, but them's the laws."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.3,
    "endTime": 153.0,
    "text": "Well, have a good day, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.1,
    "endTime": 154.2,
    "text": "Mr. Dooby Doo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.4,
    "endTime": 162.20000000000002,
    "text": "I'm Norvel, but everyone calls me Shaggy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.3,
    "endTime": 163.4,
    "text": "Raggy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.3,
    "endTime": 165.9,
    "text": "No, it's Shaggy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.2,
    "endTime": 168.2,
    "text": "That's what I said. Raggy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.7,
    "endTime": 169.89999999999998,
    "text": "We'll work on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.6,
    "endTime": 178.5,
    "text": "Shaggy, you and your new friend better hurry up if you want to trick-or-treat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.6,
    "endTime": 180.29999999999998,
    "text": "Yay! Okay, Mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.9,
    "endTime": 182.3,
    "text": "Let me show you my room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.2,
    "endTime": 196.29999999999998,
    "text": "Who's that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.9,
    "endTime": 200.9,
    "text": "This is Blue Falcon; he's half man, half falcon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.2,
    "endTime": 204.2,
    "text": "What's this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.3,
    "endTime": 206.20000000000002,
    "text": "It's a bed; you sleep in it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.4,
    "endTime": 214.20000000000002,
    "text": "Soft! I've never had a bed before."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.7,
    "endTime": 218.2,
    "text": "In fact, I've never had anything before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.9,
    "endTime": 224.20000000000002,
    "text": "I ran out this afternoon and I got something for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.6,
    "endTime": 231.29999999999998,
    "text": "I know we just met and I didn't want to seem too desperate or, you know, come on too strong, but..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.6,
    "endTime": 238.6,
    "text": "I love it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.6,
    "endTime": 245.5,
    "text": "I promise I'll never take it off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.5,
    "endTime": 255.0,
    "text": "As long as we have each other, we'll be just fine on our own."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.7,
    "endTime": 258.7,
    "text": "Uh..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.8,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "What's the hold up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.1,
    "endTime": 262.3,
    "text": "The ball return won't return our ball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.4,
    "endTime": 273.2,
    "text": "Oh, there it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.3,
    "endTime": 275.2,
    "text": "Zoinks!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.9,
    "endTime": 277.9,
    "text": "Like, what is going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.8,
    "endTime": 284.40000000000003,
    "text": "No offense, but I think I like you better as a bowling ball!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.5,
    "endTime": 285.5,
    "text": "Me, too!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.7,
    "endTime": 289.9,
    "text": "Look out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.2,
    "endTime": 296.2,
    "text": "What now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.3,
    "endTime": 297.40000000000003,
    "text": "Follow my lead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.3,
    "endTime": 299.7,
    "text": "Who's hungry?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.8,
    "endTime": 301.5,
    "text": "Check out the specials!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.0,
    "endTime": 305.2,
    "text": "So, like, what are you guys in the mood to eat?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.3,
    "endTime": 306.90000000000003,
    "text": "And please don't say human."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.0,
    "endTime": 308.3,
    "text": "Or dog."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.5,
    "endTime": 314.9,
    "text": "Okay, bowling alley yakatori."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.0,
    "endTime": 316.3,
    "text": "And how about you guys?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.4,
    "endTime": 317.5,
    "text": "Hot wings to share?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.4,
    "endTime": 320.79999999999995,
    "text": "Got it. And for you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.7,
    "endTime": 325.09999999999997,
    "text": "Oh, no! We're out of calamari!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.4,
    "endTime": 333.59999999999997,
    "text": "Did we lose them?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.2,
    "endTime": 335.7,
    "text": "[I'm] Pretty sure we didn't!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.5,
    "endTime": 346.3,
    "text": "Looks like this is goodbye, old buddy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.5,
    "endTime": 348.5,
    "text": "I never saw Paris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.9,
    "endTime": 351.79999999999995,
    "text": "Huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.0,
    "endTime": 374.4,
    "text": "Oh, man! Dig that crazy elevator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.5,
    "endTime": 375.9,
    "text": "You okay, Scooby Doo?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.0,
    "endTime": 377.9,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.0,
    "endTime": 381.4,
    "text": "Where are we?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.7,
    "endTime": 389.9,
    "text": "- Do you realize where we are?  - No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 390.0,
    "endTime": 391.3,
    "text": "Look around, man!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.4,
    "endTime": 395.5,
    "text": "The clean modern aesthetic, the cool blue color palette, we're in..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.6,
    "endTime": 397.6,
    "text": "- IKEA!  - ... the Falcon Fury!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 397.7,
    "endTime": 398.7,
    "text": "Did you say IKEA?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.8,
    "endTime": 401.3,
    "text": "Nope. I said Falcon Fury, just like you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.4,
    "endTime": 404.79999999999995,
    "text": "Scoob, somebody thinks we're important enough to...."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.1,
    "endTime": 406.8,
    "text": "It's nice to be wanted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.1,
    "endTime": 408.40000000000003,
    "text": "Ow! What was that for?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.5,
    "endTime": 410.1,
    "text": "Making sure this isn't a dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.2,
    "endTime": 412.2,
    "text": "You're supposed to pinch yourself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.5,
    "endTime": 419.5,
    "text": "Finished?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.9,
    "endTime": 420.79999999999995,
    "text": "- Ow!  - Yes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.9,
    "endTime": 423.79999999999995,
    "text": "Uh, guys? Adventure's calling, and it's for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.8,
    "endTime": 429.8,
    "text": "Hello, adventure. Yes, will you take my name and number off your list?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.3,
    "endTime": 433.6,
    "text": "But Raggy, this is our chance!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.7,
    "endTime": 435.7,
    "text": "- You really want to do this?  - Uh-huh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.8,
    "endTime": 437.7,
    "text": "Well, I'm not gonna let you do it without me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 437.8,
    "endTime": 441.2,
    "text": "After all, there is no \"I\" in Scooby and Shaggy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.3,
    "endTime": 443.8,
    "text": "Wait, is there? No. All good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.2,
    "endTime": 445.3,
    "text": "- We're in!  - We're in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 445.4,
    "endTime": 446.9,
    "text": "That's what I'm talking about."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.0,
    "endTime": 451.5,
    "text": "FYI, you are officially out of... everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452.7,
    "endTime": 454.5,
    "text": "Yes! I love these guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.0,
    "endTime": 458.4,
    "text": "Prepare your taste buds for a Scoob Shag specialty."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.0,
    "endTime": 466.0,
    "text": "Whoa! You put jalapeño peppers on your ice cream?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.1,
    "endTime": 467.1,
    "text": "Heat and sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.2,
    "endTime": 469.2,
    "text": "It's our signature dessert."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.8,
    "endTime": 479.7,
    "text": "Hustle, you two, we haven't got all day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.2,
    "endTime": 483.3,
    "text": "Second thoughts?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.4,
    "endTime": 486.79999999999995,
    "text": "Honestly, buddy? I'm on my fourth or fifth thoughts."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.3,
    "endTime": 495.7,
    "text": "Oh, man. This amusement park isn't very amusing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.8,
    "endTime": 503.1,
    "text": "Hey! Did Dastardly get the anonymous tip, too?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.6,
    "endTime": 505.40000000000003,
    "text": "- This way!  - Yikes!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.4,
    "endTime": 541.8,
    "text": "Haha, weak link, my butt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.3,
    "endTime": 551.5999999999999,
    "text": "Whoa, dude, what do you want with us?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.1,
    "endTime": 556.5,
    "text": "I don't care about you; you're not remotely important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.6,
    "endTime": 558.2,
    "text": "It's the dog I need."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.4,
    "endTime": 564.4,
    "text": "Stay! Sit! Kneel! Did nobody train this thing?"
  }
]